         <abstract id="aspace_51764b097058364c115538aff8c55db6">The Helen Wright Papers consist primarily of letters from Myra Hess and Teresa Carreño. They also contain photographs, clippings, and miscellaneous items.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <persname identifier="dts_a3e0ff54c16f264f87ce6b4ffef512d3bf447c41" source="naf">
